'''''Somewhere in Africa: The Cries of humanity''''' ni film y'ikinamico yo muri [[Gana]]  ya 2011<ref>http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/853577762</ref>, iyobowe na Frank Rajah Arase, yakinwe na Majid Michel, Martha Ankomah na Kofi Adjorlolo<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Somewhere_in_Africa</ref><ref>https://www.ghmoviefreak.com/stage-play-somewhere-africa-adapted-theater/</ref>. Yakiriye kandidatire 7 mu bihembo bya 9 bya Afurika Movie Academy Awards harimo ibyiciro: Umukinnyi witwaye neza mu nshingano zambere, Ibyagezweho mu majwi, Ibyagezweho mu ngaruka ziboneka no kugerwaho na Make-Up. Majid Michel niwe wahawe igihembo cyonyine cya film<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201106241193.html</ref><ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/308809282_Film_as_an_agent_of_Human_Rights_Advancement_in_Nigeria_A_study_of_Bloody_Night_and_Somewhere_in_Africa</ref>.

