== Kwakira ==
Nollywood Reinvented yayihaye amanota 43%, ashima amajwi yayo, cinematografi hamwe namashusho<ref>https://mcutimes.com/Movies/titles/310842/somewhere-in-africa</ref>. 

== Ibihembo ==
Yakiriye kandidatire 7 mu bihembo bya 9 bya Afurika Movie Academy Awards ku byiciro: Ibyagezweho mu Gushushanya Umusaruro, Ibyagezweho mu Gushushanya Imyambarire, Ibyagezweho muri Make-Up, Ibyagezweho mu majwi, Ibyagezweho mu mashusho, Umukinnyi mwiza / Umukinnyi utanga ikizere, n'umukinnyi mwiza muri  Uruhare Rukuru. Majid Michel niwe wahawe igihembo cyonyine cya film<ref>https://www.modernghana.com/entertainment/15494/somewhere-in-africa-is-significant-to-africans.html</ref><ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.person.frank-rajah-arase.32456.html</ref>.

